:: Intro - Debt Question [ev-therapist-2]
You shuffle in the bed, arching your back to better reposition yourself with your... newfound distribution of weight. Looking at the guard, you´re reminded by the words "debt" and "punishment". With a slight break in your voice, you question your debt... and what happens if you don´t pay.
<<= setup.speak($characters.drlinus, "The cost of maintaining your outdated cryo chamber has caused your debt to accumulate over time. As well as your required transformation into a more suitable subject for debt repayment, by law of course.")>>
You scuff as you clench your fist, almost boiling over again, you just manage to calm yourself down.
<<= setup.speak($player, "I literally paid for this... Myself?")>><<= setup.speak($characters.drlinus, "Of course... That´s only fair you know. Your debt as it stands is $player.debt units, which is... Wow... Just wow.")>>
Biting your lip, your stomach drops at the sound of the figure.
<<= setup.speak($player, "That sounds really high...")>><<= setup.speak($characters.drlinus, "It is... But... Not entirely impossible to repay. You should be able to repay it over time with some help. We take care of our own at eVentia, we´re family now! Of course!... Anything else?")>>
Knowing yourself, you resort yourself to asking the question; What if you don´t pay at all?
<<= setup.speak($characters.drlinus, "Well... You would never be able to apply for citizenship... And... Errr... If you don´t at the very least pay your interest. It may have dire consequences.")>><<= setup.speak($player, "Consequences? Like... What would happen? Jail?")>>
He clears his throat as he elaborates.
<<= setup.speak($characters.drlinus, "No. We handle all internal conflicts... Internally. Firstly, I highly suggest you do not challenge this, and pay the interest. If not, the higher ups might force you to go on the block. Which would be highly ill-advised.")>>
The guard chuckles in the background, but are swiftly shushed by Dr. Linus.
<<= setup.speak($characters.drlinus, "It would most likely result in your loss of your virginity, which has some real value on the auction blocks.")>><<= setup.speak($player, "SAY WHAT?!")>><<= setup.speak($characters.drlinus, "Well, no one is forcing you here! At least yet...")>>
You sit back down after having sprung up and cross your arms in disapprovement.

