:: Intro - Home Question [ev-therapist-2]
Thinking back on your old apartment, your stomach churns as you already get a sense of homesickness.
<<= setup.speak($player,"What about my home? Where will I be staying? I bet it´s gone now.")>>
<<= setup.speak($characters.drlinus, "It most definitely is, however, eVentia provides all baseline Event Girls with their own standard housing pod, conveniently located together in the entertainment center.")>> 
